items.headline: Learn how to Protect Your iPhone and iPad with Apple iOS Restriction Controls, Guided Access, Find My iPhone & iPad!
objectives_summary: Become a Master of your iPad, iPhone, and iPod Touch by learning all of Apple’s Amazing Builtin iOS Parental Controls:
1. Configure Parental Control Restrictions - Content Control, Privacy Control. Protections for both kids and the owner of the Apple Mobile Device.

2.  Configure Guided Access - Locking Mobile device into one app. Setting Time Limits for Use. Prevent touching certain areas of the screen or entire screen. Hardware lockdown features like preventing keyboard, volume, and sleep/wake adjustments.
